name: Around the Corner
description:
As we continue our walk, we go around the corner and see a signpost covered with sticker art. We realize that the stickers are a template for a new reality.

#2 in my graffiti series, this is a iphone scan of some of my fave sticker art. I dropped it into my video feedback and synthesis system. There are 4 layers of video signal interacting with each other, captured live.
